  <entry>
    <title>Hexo+Github建立博客教程</title>
    <link href="http://ly1t1f.github.io/2020/01/17/Hexo-Github%E5%BB%BA%E7%AB%8B%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/"/>
    <id>http://ly1t1f.github.io/2020/01/17/Hexo-Github%E5%BB%BA%E7%AB%8B%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/</id>
    <published>2020-01-17T14:09:16.000Z</published>
    <updated>2020-01-18T08:50:29.601Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<ul><li><a href="#前言">前言</a></li><li><a href="#Hexo+GitHub">Hexo+GitHub</a></li><li><a href="#搭建环境">搭建环境</a></li><li><a href="#配置GitHub">配置GitHub</a></li><li><a href="#初始化博客">初始化博客</a></li><li><a href="#发表文章">发表文章</a></li></ul><h2 id="前言"><a href="#前言" class="headerlink" title="前言"></a>前言</h2><h4 id="一、前言"><a href="#一、前言" class="headerlink" title="一、前言"></a>一、前言</h4><p>为什么要建立博客，如果使用果平台博客如博客园等，就会发现有一个自己的博客，就会极为方便，不受约束，没有广告，布局也可以有着自己的想法。所以有自己的博客是一件很酷的事。</p><h2 id="Hexo-GitHub"><a href="#Hexo-GitHub" class="headerlink" title="Hexo+GitHub"></a>Hexo+GitHub</h2><h4 id="二、Hexo-GitHub"><a href="#二、Hexo-GitHub" class="headerlink" title="二、Hexo+GitHub"></a>二、Hexo+GitHub</h4><p>为什么选择Hexo+GitHub，因为成本较低，只有学习成本;<br>GitHub_Pages会提供免费空间，并会提供username.github.io的默认域名，则不需要购买服务器和域名。</p><h2 id="搭建环境"><a href="#搭建环境" class="headerlink" title="搭建环境"></a>搭建环境</h2><h4 id="三、搭建环境"><a href="#三、搭建环境" class="headerlink" title="三、搭建环境"></a>三、搭建环境</h4><h5 id="1、系统：ubuntu18-04"><a href="#1、系统：ubuntu18-04" class="headerlink" title="1、系统：ubuntu18.04"></a>1、系统：ubuntu18.04</h5><h5 id="2、安装node-js"><a href="#2、安装node-js" class="headerlink" title="2、安装node.js"></a>2、安装node.js</h5><p>在终端下输入：sudo apt-get install nodejs，安装完成即可</p><h5 id="3、安装git"><a href="#3、安装git" class="headerlink" title="3、安装git"></a>3、安装git</h5><p>终端输入sudo apt-get install git，安装完成即可</p><p>git安装完成后输入以下命令：</p><figure class="highlight routeros"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git<span class="built_in"> config </span>--global user.name <span class="string">"username"</span></span><br><span class="line">git<span class="built_in"> config </span>--global user.email <span class="string">"username@xx.com"</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>username和email均为自己的GitHub的注册名和邮箱</strong></p><p><img src="https://imgconvert.csdnimg.cn/aHR0cHM6Ly9waWMyLnpoaW1nLmNvbS92Mi1mNTdhNDY2MjJjYTYzYjc1NmZkN2NmYjkxMTk3NGVlZF9yLmpwZw?x-oss-process=image/format,png" alt="git命令"></p><h5 id="4、安装Hexo"><a href="#4、安装Hexo" class="headerlink" title="4、安装Hexo"></a>4、安装Hexo</h5><p>使用npm安装Hexo</p><p>终端下输入：<br><code>npm install -g hexo-cli</code></p><h2 id="配置GitHub"><a href="#配置GitHub" class="headerlink" title="配置GitHub"></a>配置GitHub</h2><h4 id="四、配置GitHub"><a href="#四、配置GitHub" class="headerlink" title="四、配置GitHub"></a>四、配置GitHub</h4><h5 id="1、注册登录GitHub"><a href="#1、注册登录GitHub" class="headerlink" title="1、注册登录GitHub"></a>1、注册登录GitHub</h5><p>创建新的仓库<br>,右上角选择<code>Create a new repository</code>，命名为<code>username.github.io</code><br>[外链图片转存失败,源站可能有防盗链机制,建议将图片保存下来直接上传(img-PPPofdua-1579064711158)(<a href="https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-d7ffab98b05bbb00ce9602c6f8d0ce70_hd.jpg" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-d7ffab98b05bbb00ce9602c6f8d0ce70_hd.jpg</a>  “仓库”)]</p><h5 id="2、添加仓库密匙"><a href="#2、添加仓库密匙" class="headerlink" title="2、添加仓库密匙"></a>2、添加仓库密匙</h5><p>在终端下输入：<br><code>ssh-keygen -t rsa -C &quot;Github的注册邮箱地址&quot;</code><br>一直enter即可完成，密匙生成完成后， 会得到  <code>id_rsa</code>和<code>id_rsa.pub</code>两个文件，打开id_rsa.pub文件并复制其内容；<br>打开<a href="https://github.com/settings/ssh" target="_blank" rel="noopener">密匙设置链接</a><br><img src="https://imgconvert.csdnimg.cn/aHR0cHM6Ly9waWM0LnpoaW1nLmNvbS84MC92Mi0xMDc4OTg4ODJkZjZkOWU3MWNlZDVjM2Y4NGNhYTJiZl9oZC5qcGc?x-oss-process=image/format,png" alt=""></p><p>将刚刚复制的内容复制到<code>key</code>对话框中，<code>title</code>可随意命名，点击<code>Add SSH Key</code>配置完成</p><h2 id="初始化博客"><a href="#初始化博客" class="headerlink" title="初始化博客"></a>初始化博客</h2><h4 id="五、初始化博客"><a href="#五、初始化博客" class="headerlink" title="五、初始化博客"></a>五、初始化博客</h4><h5 id="1、建立本地存储文档"><a href="#1、建立本地存储文档" class="headerlink" title="1、建立本地存储文档"></a>1、建立本地存储文档</h5><p>建立一个新的文件夹Blog，在本文件夹中打开终端，输入：<br><code>sudo hexo init blog</code>    </p><p>若显示以下命令，则新建成功：            </p><p><code>INFO Start blogging with Hexo!</code><br>接着执行以下命令：</p><figure class="highlight verilog"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo hexo <span class="keyword">generate</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">sudo hexo server</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>若显示：</p><figure class="highlight pgsql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">INFO</span>  <span class="keyword">Start</span> processing</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">INFO</span>  Hexo <span class="keyword">is</span> running at http://localhost:<span class="number">4000</span>/. Press Ctrl+C <span class="keyword">to</span> stop.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>本地服务器则成功启动了，在浏览器中输入：localhost:4000,就能看到初步模样了<br><img src="https://imgconvert.csdnimg.cn/aHR0cHM6Ly9waWMzLnpoaW1nLmNvbS84MC92Mi1jNjkzZTljMTliZWFhYjIzNTBiZWJkNWJlMjU1MjM2Ml9oZC5qcGc?x-oss-process=image/format,png" alt=""></p><h5 id="2、部署到Github"><a href="#2、部署到Github" class="headerlink" title="2、部署到Github"></a>2、部署到Github</h5><p>Blog文件夹下生成了一个文件夹blog，打开里面的_config文件夹,并修改参数信息：    </p><ul><li><strong>修改网站相关信息</strong>：<figure class="highlight avrasm"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="symbol">title:</span> 标题</span><br><span class="line"><span class="symbol">subtitle:</span> 签名</span><br><span class="line"><span class="symbol">description:</span> 网页描述</span><br><span class="line"><span class="symbol">author:</span> yangyps</span><br><span class="line"><span class="symbol">language:</span> <span class="built_in">zh</span>-CN</span><br><span class="line"><span class="symbol">timezone:</span> Asia/Shanghai</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><strong>配置部署</strong>：<figure class="highlight groovy"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">deploy:</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">type:</span> git</span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">repo:</span> <span class="string">https:</span><span class="comment">//github.com/username/username.github.io.git</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">branch:</span> master</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><p>也可以将repo修改成以下格式：</p><p><code>repo: https://用户名:密码@github.com/用户名/用户名.github.io.git</code></p><p>这样<code>hexo delpoy</code>的时候就不需要输入账号和密码了</p><p><strong>==注意==</strong>：==在每个参数的:后都需要有一个空格==</p><ul><li><strong>配置统一资源定位符</strong>：</li></ul><p><code>url: https://username.github.io</code><br>其他信息如：root（根目录）、permalink（永久链接）、permalink_defaults（默认永久链接）都保持默认</p><h2 id="发表文章"><a href="#发表文章" class="headerlink" title="发表文章"></a>发表文章</h2><h4 id="六、发表文章"><a href="#六、发表文章" class="headerlink" title="六、发表文章"></a>六、发表文章</h4><h5 id="1、创建文章"><a href="#1、创建文章" class="headerlink" title="1、创建文章"></a>1、创建文章</h5><p>终端输入：</p><p><code>sudo hexo new &quot;新建文章名&quot;</code></p><p>==注意：新建的文章要用Markdown文法编写==</p><h5 id="2、编写文章"><a href="#2、编写文章" class="headerlink" title="2、编写文章"></a>2、编写文章</h5><p>在\Blog\blog\source_posts\新建文章名.md下打开新建的文件</p><p>文章的一开始处，可以按如下格式添加文章标题，日期，分类、标签以及描述等：</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">---</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">title:</span> <span class="string">title</span> <span class="comment">#文章标题</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">date:</span> <span class="number">2017</span><span class="number">-09</span><span class="number">-08</span> <span class="number">23</span><span class="string">:47:44</span> <span class="comment">#文章生成时间</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">categories:</span> <span class="string">"Hexo教程"</span> <span class="comment">#文章分类目录 可以省略</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">tags:</span> <span class="comment">#文章标签 可以省略</span></span><br><span class="line">         <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="string">标签1</span></span><br><span class="line">         <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="string">标签2</span></span><br><span class="line">     <span class="attr">description:</span> <span class="comment">#你对本页的描述 可以省略</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">---</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h5 id="3、发表文章"><a href="#3、发表文章" class="headerlink" title="3、发表文章"></a>3、发表文章</h5><p>在blog目录下，输入如下的一系列命令：</p><figure class="highlight pgsql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo clean</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">INFO</span>  Deleted <span class="keyword">database</span>.</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">INFO</span>  Deleted <span class="built_in">public</span> folder.</span><br><span class="line">$ hexo generate</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">INFO</span>  <span class="keyword">Start</span> processing</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">INFO</span>  Files loaded <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="number">1.48</span> s</span><br><span class="line">#省略</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">INFO</span>  <span class="number">29</span> files <span class="keyword">generated</span> <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="number">4.27</span> s</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">$ hexo <span class="keyword">server</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">INFO</span>  <span class="keyword">Start</span> processing</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">INFO</span>  Hexo <span class="keyword">is</span> running at http://localhost:<span class="number">4000</span>/. Press Ctrl+C <span class="keyword">to</span> stop.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>打开<a href="http://localhost:4000/，可以在本地预览网站的初步样子。" target="_blank" rel="noopener">http://localhost:4000/，可以在本地预览网站的初步样子。</a><br>最后一步，发布到远程，执行hexo deploy</p><figure class="highlight routeros"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo deploy</span><br><span class="line">   <span class="builtin-name">INFO</span>  Deploying: git</span><br><span class="line">   <span class="builtin-name">INFO</span>  Clearing .deploy_git folder<span class="built_in">..</span>.</span><br><span class="line">   <span class="builtin-name">INFO</span>  Copying files <span class="keyword">from</span> public folder<span class="built_in">..</span>.</span><br><span class="line">   #省略</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>到此为止，博客已经初步建立完成    </p>]]></content>
    
